[I] An E17 system monitor

[T] Evisum is a system monitor using EFL. It's pretty and pays homage to FOSS
[T] applications from the 90s. Support for processes, process, CPU, memory,
[T] sensors and networking.

[U] https://www.enlightenment.org

[A] Alastair Roy Poole <netstar@gmail.com>
